---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Help Center - The Davinci Project" description="Get help with The Davinci Project.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Help Center</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Find answers to common questions and get support.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      
      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What is The Davinci Project?</h3>
          <p>The Davinci Project is a digital asset transfer escrow protocol that provides reliability and safety for cryptocurrency transactions. We act as a trusted intermediary to ensure secure transfers between parties.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How does the escrow protocol work?</h3>
          <p>When a transaction is initiated, funds are held in a multi-signature escrow account. Once all conditions are met and both parties confirm the transaction, the funds are released to the recipient.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Which cryptocurrencies are supported?</h3>
          <p>We support major cryptocurrencies including Bitcoin (BTC), Ethereum (ETH), and various ERC-20 tokens. Check our documentation for the full list of supported assets.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Is my data secure?</h3>
          <p>Yes, we use industry-standard security practices including multi-signature wallets, encryption, and regular security audits to protect your assets and data.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How can I integrate with my platform?</h3>
          <p>We provide comprehensive APIs and SDKs for easy integration. Visit our API documentation to get started, or contact our support team for assistance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2>Still Need Help?</h2>
      <p>Can't find what you're looking for? Our support team is here to help.</p>
      <a href="mailto:support@davinciproject.net" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Support</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-primary) 0%, var(--bg-secondary) 100%);
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  
  .content-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }
  
  .content-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .faq-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }
  
  .faq-item {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .faq-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .faq-item p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }
  
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent-green);
    color: #000;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .page-hero {
      padding: 7rem 0 3rem;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .container {
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
